project_descr: Resilience oriented information systems for improved decision making. (Programa de Sistemas de información para la Resiliencia en Seguridad Alimentaria y Nutricional de la region del SICA-PROGRESAN-SICA).

outputs.output_descr: Improved availability of regular, timely and early warning information as well as evidence-based analysis regarding to food and nutrition security, nutrition and resilience situation for decision making.
